================================================================
Data & Confidentiality Notice
================================================================

All business data shipped with this repository (under
`public/data/demo/`) has been thoroughly desensitized:

  - Project names → Greek letter codenames (项目 Alpha / Eta / ...)
  - Employee identifiers → opaque IDs (E-XXX)
  - Department identifiers → opaque codes (P-XX)
  - Profit / revenue figures → uniformly scaled and randomly
    perturbed; not real financial figures
  - Compensation percentile (CR) → public-industry P50/P75 proxy

The desensitized data is provided strictly to demonstrate the
product's analytical pipeline. It MUST NOT be interpreted as real
business performance of any company, nor reverse-engineered to
infer underlying business metrics.

